text: Paris-Michael Katherine Jackson (born April 3, 1998) is an American model and actress. Jackson is the second and only daughter of Michael Jackson and Debbie Rowe. == Early Life == Paris was born at Spalding Pain Clinic in Beverly Hills, California, She is the second child and only daughter of Michael Jackson and Debbie Rowe, She had one brother is Prince Jackson and one half brother is Blanket Jackson. == References == Category:1998 births Category:Pansexual people Category:Living people Category:Michael Jackson Category:Models from California Category:Actors from Beverly Hills, California
